This story is the Post-Crisis on Infinite Earths reboot of Hal Jordan's origin and how he became Green Lantern. Parts of it have been retconned as of Green Lantern v4 29-35 (Secret Origin), but it is still a great read and worth checking out if you are a Hal Jordan fan. I have also included the famous issue of DC Showcase 22 which was the original origin + debut of Hal Jordan, for comparison/nostalgic value/entertainment. It's not a bad read and frankly I prefer DC's older stuff to Marvel more and more. Anywho, these are high quality scans thanks Minutemen-KangCouncil, and though I don't believe they are digital they might as well be to the naked eye. Hoe you enjoy, please seed - thanks! :-)
